org.factcenter.qilin.protocols.generic

Class OTExtensionServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.factcenter.qilin.protocols.generic.ProtocolPartyBase
      • org.factcenter.qilin.protocols.generic.OTExtensionServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, ProtocolParty

    public class OTExtensionServer
extends ProtocolPartyBase
implements java.lang.Runnable
    A Server that handles the generation of precomputed OTs. Note that the server must have a separate communication channel from clients in a different thread so that OTs can be generated asynchronously.
